                "Row 1 × Col 2: (5)(−1/7) + (2)(5/14) = −5/7 + 10/14 = −10/14 + 10/14 = 0 ✓",
                "Row 2 × Col 1: (3)(2/7) + (4)(−3/14) = 6/7 − 12/14 = 12/14 − 12/14 = 0 ✓",
                "Row 2 × Col 2: (3)(−1/7) + (4)(5/14) = −3/7 + 20/14 = −6/14 + 20/14 = 14/14 = 1 ✓",
