                    "Step 2 — Amplitude: |a| = 3",
                    "Step 3 — Period: 360°/b = 360°/2 = 180°",
                    "Step 4 — Phase shift: −c/b. Rewrite as 2(x − 30°): phase shift = +30° to the right",
                    "Step 5 — Vertical shift: d = 1 (midline is y = 1)",
