        create:     "A circle passes through the three points A(1,7), B(7,1), and C(−1,1). Set up the three simultaneous equations in the expanded form x²+y²+2gx+2fy+c=0, solve the system to find g, f, and c, write the circle equation in both expanded and centre-radius forms, and verify that all three given points satisfy the equation."
