                        position: "Both between the two parallel lines; one left of transversal, one right",
                        theorem: "If lines are parallel, alternate interior angles are equal",
                        converse: "If alternate interior angles are equal, the lines are parallel",
                        notation: "∠3 = ∠6 (alt. int. ∠s, AB ∥ CD)",
