                        "Square: 360/4 = 90°",
                        "Regular pentagon: 360/5 = 72°",
                        "Regular hexagon: 360/6 = 60°",
                        "Regular octagon: 360/8 = 45°",
                        "Regular decagon: 360/10 = 36°"
