                        "Area = ½(a+b)(a+b) = ½(a+b)²",
                        "Also = three triangles: ½ab + ½ab + ½c²",
                        "½(a²+2ab+b²) = ab + ½c²",
                        "a² + 2ab + b² = 2ab + c²",
